  "author": "XO_OX Designs",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "description": "A chamber-like sine + triangle pad with prominent formant filtering — at JOURNEY 0.32 it has vocal qualities, recognizably human. The formant morph position shifts as JOURNEY rises, and at 0.72 the Climax unfolds over an unusually long 3-second bloom — the vowel drifts from familiar resonance into something inhuman. Like hearing a chorus gradually become a single continuous tone that was never sung by a throat.",
